{"tid":2331452,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港究竟點撚樣買漫畫","createTime":"2020-12-18T20:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T08:20:39.000Z","uid":213328,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6a2ca47b9a9398851ff696fe1dbe16be59e60c","tid":2331452,"uid":213328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T20:09:58.000Z","msg":"講緊中文翻譯嘅日本漫畫<br />\n<br />\n可以落後到連上網買漫畫嘅途徑都冇<br />\n乜乜香港書城網上書店嗰啲又唔賣漫畫<br />\n<br />\n就算去信和 啲書冷門少少都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅日本漫畫代理商點樣賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def67c59c1be9f364e6ab47c618e5a7ef2e9d9b9","tid":2331452,"uid":18877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"電子版可以去Book Walker<br />\n實體書可以去台灣網上書店 有啲會送去香港<br />\n金石堂，博客來果啲"},{"pid":"663c55d4c72b59fef42f352a72ea9b3dbc1da5a4","tid":2331452,"uid":17678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"漫畫鋪/信和"},{"pid":"52278a872363f2c2886eade1354af0174428ae97","tid":2331452,"uid":87394,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:54:23.000Z","msg":"冷門都賣就真係唔洗賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd394e8be4980836752fb65e26b76a4143523aa6","tid":2331452,"uid":367266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"二樓書店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3e17801e917092c13fa4e0fbdc149630e91772","tid":2331452,"uid":181774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T02:41:58.000Z","msg":"本身香港代理嘅業務公司都收晒皮咁濟<br />\n係咪得返玉皇朝?&nbsp;都代理得少漫畫<br />\n其他繁中都去晒台版代理<br />\n漫畫舖全港都執得八八九九<br />\n就算我宜家買輕小說<br />\n一係出信和買,&nbsp;一係等夠幾本係金石堂&nbsp;/&nbsp;博客來買算"},{"pid":"1253b9c23f41fceb3ec27fba53aec0a7bc497f45","tid":2331452,"uid":17678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e3e17801e917092c13fa4e0fbdc149630e91772","tid":2331452,"uid":181774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,